item.title: Michelle add a quote by Dr. Seuss
item.description: "You have brains in your head. You have feet in your shoes. You can steer yourself any direction you choose. You're on your own. And you know what you know. And YOU are the one who'll decide where to go..." -- Dr. Seuss

item.title: Michelle add a quote by Helen Fielding
item.description: "It is a truth universally acknowledged that when one part of your life starts going okay, another falls spectacularly to pieces." -- Helen Fielding

item.title: Michelle add a quote by Helen Fielding
item.description: "I will not fall for any of the following: alcoholics, workaholics, commitment phobics, people with girlfriends or wives, misogynists, megalomanics, chauvists, emotional fuckwits or freeloaders, perverts." -- Helen Fielding

item.title: Michelle add a quote by Helen Fielding
item.description: "I realize it has become too easy to find a diet to fit in with whatever you happen to feel like eating and that diets are not there to be picked and mixed but picked and stuck to, which is exactly what I shall begin to do once I've eaten this chocolate croissant." -- Helen Fielding
